d+EPO+which+began+with+Pension+Benefits+is+affirmed.+Thus%2c+it+could+be+analysed+that+the+case+law+prior+to+Pension+Benefit+still+relevant+in+the+UK.+%e2%80%9cAny+hardware+approach%e2%80%9d+differs+from+the+UK+approach+in+regard+to+the+way+invention+is+analysed+and+the+way+technical+character+is+determined.+The+UK+rejects+the+confer+on+non-technical+activity+when+determining+technical+character+unlike+the+EPO+approach.34%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e3.+ALICE+IN+THE+UK%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThis+part+will+examine+how+US+can+benefit+from+the+UK+and+the+EU+in+order+to+ensure+international+harmonization.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAlthough+the+US+courts+have+made+different+decisions+in+post-Alice+as+mentioned+above%2c+Supreme+Court%e2%80%99s+ruling+in+Alice+case+on+patentability+of+computer-implemented+inventions+is+in+the+parallel+path+with+the+UK+and+the+EU.+Patent+practitioners+in+the+UK+and+the+EU+may+realise+the+similar+framework+set+forth+in+US+Supreme+Court%e2%80%99s+Alice.35%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAs+stated+in+Benson36+earlier%2c+computer+program+itself+is+excluded+from+patentable+subject+matter.+As+it+is+known%2c+computer-implemented+inventions+work+by+software+or+programming.+And+Alice+states+that+%e2%80%9can+invention+implemented+by+software+involves+an+abstract+idea%e2%80%9d.37+Thus%2c+computer-implemented+invention+in+the+event+that+computer+is+generic%2c+first+part+of+the+Alice+test+is+done+namely+software+identifies+the+%e2%80%9cabstract+idea%e2%80%9d.38%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAs+a+second+and+last+part+of+this+test%2c+court+should+search+for+an+%e2%80%9cinventive+concept%e2%80%9d.+This+part+of+the%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b30+CaseT-931%2f95%2c+Controlling+Pension+Benefit+Systems+Partnership%2fPBS+PARTNERSHIP%2c+%5b2001%5d+O.J.E.P.O.+441%2c+448+(Technical+Bd.+Appeal+3.5.01%2c+Sept.+8%2c+2000)%26nbsp%3b31+Case+T-258%2f03%2c+Auction+Method%2fHITACHI%2c+%5b2004%5d+O.J.E.P.O.+575%2c+587+(Technical+Bd.+Appeal+3.5.01%2c+Apr.+21%2c+2004)%26nbsp%3b32+Case+T-424%2f03%2c+MICROSOFT%2fClipboard+Formats+I%2c+%5b2006%5d+E.P.O.R.+414%2c+417+(Technical+Bd.+Appeal+3.5.01%2c+Feb.+23%2c+2006)%26nbsp%3b33+Aerotel+Ltd.+v.+Telco+Holdings+Ltd.%2c+%5b2006%5d+EWCA+(Civ)+1371%2c+%5b40%5d+(Eng.).%26nbsp%3b34+Lionel+Bently%2c+Brad+Sherman%2c+Intellectual+Property+Law+(4th+edn%2c+OUP+2014)+35+Brendon+Beheshti%2c+%e2%80%98Getting+beyond+Abstract+Confusion%3a+How+the+United+Kingdom%27s+Jurisprudence+Can+Aid+in+Developing+an+Analytic+Framework+for+Patent-Eligibility+in+Light+of+Alice+v.+CLS+Bank%e2%80%99+(2014)10+Wash.+J.+L.+Tech.+%26amp%3b+Arts%2c+138%26nbsp%3b36+Benson+(n+4)+37+Alice+(n+2)+38+Behesti+(n+35)+148.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3etest+pretty+similar+to+European+and+particularly+the+UK+approach+regarding+patentability+requirements.+For+this+reason%2c+the+UK%e2%80%99s+patent+jurisprudence+could+be+useful%2c+instructive+and+informative+in+this+regard.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eWhile+the+EU+approach+provides+patent-ineligible+items+in+a+direct+and+explicit+way%2c+the+US+approach+defines+patent-eligible+subject+matter+and+then+provides+exceptions.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eEngland+and+Wales+Court+of+Appeal+declared+four-step+test+for+determination+of+patent-eligibility+in+Aerotel.+When+the+steps+in+Aerotel+examined%2c+it+could+be+directly+noticed+that+framework+applied+in+the+UK+pretty+similar+with+US+Supreme+Court%e2%80%99s+ruling+in+Alice.39%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThe+two-steps+test+of+the+Alice+approach+is+same+as+the+last+two+steps+of+Aerotel+approach.+The+third+step+of+Aerotel+asks+whether+claims+are+abstract+and+then%2c+if+they+are%2c+the+fourth+step+requires+to+determine+%e2%80%9cwhether+the+contribution+is+actually+technical+in+nature%e2%80%9d.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAs+mentioned+above%2c+the+Alice+requires+%e2%80%9csomething+significantly+more%e2%80%9d+in+the+second+step.+This+step+is+echoed+in+Aerotel+and+HTC+Europe40.+Based+on+these+cases+%e2%80%9csignificantly+more%e2%80%9d+must+be+interpreted+with+direct+connection+to+%e2%80%9cinventive+concept%e2%80%9d+which+should+be+identified+for+subject+matter+eligibility.+In+other+words%2c+such+improvements+should+be+sufficient+to+serve+%e2%80%9cinventive+concept%e2%80%9d41+Lord+Justice+Jacob+stated+in+Aerotel%3a+%e2%80%9c%5bI%5dt+is+an+exercise+in+judgment+probably+involving+the+problem+said+to+be+solved%2c+how+the+invention+works%2c+what+its+advantages+are.+What+has+the+inventor+really+added+to+human+knowledge+perhaps+best+sums+up+the+exercise.+The+formulation+involves+looking+at+substance+not+form.%e2%80%9d+42+The+statement+fits+very+well+into+the+discussion+provided+in+Alice+and+it+would+be+instructive+particularly+at+this+point.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThe+similarity+in+both+steps+and+objectives+of+the+older+Aerotel+to+the+Alice+constitutes+a+basis+to+see+the+UK+rulings+as+advanced+authority.+Thus%2c+it+reduces+different+national+interpretations+on+patenteligibility.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAlthough+countries+in+EU+may+have+different+interpretations+and+applications+on+the+law+regarding+patent-eligibility+of+computer-implemented+inventions%2c+in+the+great+scheme+of+things+it+could+be+said+that+they+are+in+agreement+with+each+other.+Considering+the+extensive+case+law+in+the+UK%2c+which+has+been+used+since+2006%2c+will+be+benefit+to+the+U.S.+law.+Also+considering+the+parallel+approach+would+ensure+interoperability+of+laws+across+the+Atlantic.+Increasing+interoperability+of+laws+would+reduce+the+conflict+between+differentlaws+regarding+patentable+subject+matter+of+computer-implemented+inventions.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAs+a+consequence%2c+the+%e2%80%98something+more%e2%80%99+of+Alice+is+fairly+similar+to+UK+or+European+patent+practitioner+because+the+confusion+of+the+%e2%80%98technical+requirement%e2%80%99+and+%e2%80%98inventive+step%e2%80%99+has+been+in+these+jurisdictions+for+a+long+time.+Harmonising+the+patentable+subject+matter+internationally+which+would+help+reducing+conflict+between+different+laws+and+spurring+innovation%2c+seems+possible+with+Alice.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b39+ibid+150.+40+HTC+Europe+Co.+Ltd.+v.+Apple+Inc.%2c+%5b2013%5d+EWCA+(Civ)+451%2c+%5b50%5d+(Eng.).%26nbsp%3b41+Abraham+Kasdan%2c+Can+You+Patent+Software+and+Business+Methods+in+the+U.S.+-+How+Did+We+Get+Here+and+Where+Do+We+Now+Stand%2c+(2014)+24+Fed.+Cir.+B.J.%26nbsp%3b42+Aerotel+(n+33)%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eCONCLUSION%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eIronically%2c+the+current+status+of+computer-implemented+invention+patents+in+general+remains+in+a+state+of+uncertainty+within+the+US+and+the+EU.+As+discussed+above+both+the+EPO+and+the+US+court+decisions+reduce+clarity+regarding+patentable+subject-matter+in+their+recent+rulings.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAlthough+the+US+courts+have+been+made+slightly+varying+rulings+related+to+patent-eligibility+of+computer+implemented+inventions+in+post-Alice%2c+the+US+Supreme+Court%e2%80%99s+ruling+in+Alice+stands+parallel+with+the+UK+and+the+EU.43+Thousands+of+patent+applications+before+the+USPTO+were+invalidated+by+virtue+of+Alice+and+the+patenting+of+large+number+of+computer-implemented+inventions+have+been+subjected+to+this+elimination.+However%2c+invalidating+or+eliminating+patents+is+not+a+desirable+result.+Efforts+should+be+focused+on+a+better+system+and+higher+standards+to+ensure+that+novel+patents+are+being+granted.+It+seems+that+the+US+is+improving+the+quality+of+granting+patents+regarding+computer-implemented+inventions+compared+to+the+past.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThe+US+looks+like+it+is+coming+closer+to+the+UK+with+its+%e2%80%98something+more%e2%80%99+approach+which+needs+legal+clarity+and+the+UK%e2%80%99s+patent+jurisprudence+could+be+useful%2c+instructive+and+informative+in+this+regard.+The+EU+and+the+UK+are+unlikely+to+adopt+the+US%e2%80%99s+broad+patentable+subject+matter+approach.+However%2c+the+UK+and+the+EU+may+have+encouraged+to+harmonize+policy.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThere+are+several+reform+recommendations+regarding+this+matter.+Firstly%2c+in+a+current+highly+politicized+area%2c+the+incremental+nature+of+computer-implemented+innovation+combined+with+the+absence+of+guidance+in+determining+patentable+subject+matter%2c+gives+patent+holders+the+power+to+harm+others.+Beside+that%2c+the+potential+harm+arising+from+recognition+of+business+method+and+non-innovative+software+patents+causes+the+loss+of+significant+social+welfare.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAs+it+is+seen%2c+legal+clarity+is+needed+at+first.+It+is+highly+important+to+determine+the+qualities+of+claims+which+help+stimulate+innovation.+Unclear+standards+have+negative+effects+on+industry+and+upon+the+parties.+Because+of+the+ambiguous+state+of+patentable+subject+matter+causes+unnecessary+lawsuits.+The+US+should+prevent+overly+broad+patent+recognition.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAlthough+it+could+be+arguable+from+the+perspective+of+fully+harmonization+because+of+the+unique+aspects+of+computer+industry+including+networking+effects+and+incremental+nature+of+software%2c+certain+and+clear+policies+are+needed+to+promote+the+efficiency+of+patent+law.+As+discussed+in+the+section+on+Alice+above%2c+adopting+best+practices+developed+in+other+jurisdictions+would+reduce+